subject: Daytona 500 (Auto Race)
Automobile Racing
organizations: National Assn of Stock Car Auto Racing
lead_paragraph: Terry Labonte, a two-time Nascar Sprint Cup champion, will attempt to qualify for the Feb. 15 Daytona 500 in a Toyota fielded by Prism Motorsports, co-owned by Randy Humphrey and the former Nascar driver Phil Parson.
